  "informal_statement": "For all reals a, b, c: (a+b+c)² ≤ 3(a²+b²+c²) (a power-mean bound).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "3(a²+b²+c²) - (a+b+c)² = (a-b)² + (b-c)² + (c-a)² ≥ 0. nlinarith with three square hints.",
